<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q19_v4" title="Q19_v4" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones es equivalente a 
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:msqrt>
            <m:mn>7</m:mn>
          </m:msqrt>
          <m:mo>·</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>21</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La expresión dada es el producto de <strong>dos factores 3</strong> y un factor <strong>√7</strong>, por lo que se obtiene 3 × 3 × √7 = 9√7. En cambio, <strong>3√21</strong> vale 3 × √21 y no coincide con 9√7. Por ejemplo, al cuadrar ambas expresiones se obtiene 189 para 3√21 y 567 para 9√7, así que no son equivalentes.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>9</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>7</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Al multiplicar 3√7 por 3, se multiplican los factores numéricos 3 y 3, obteniendo 9, y el factor √7 se mantiene. Entonces 3√7 · 3 = 9√7.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>63</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La expresión original es 3√7 · 3 = 9√7. Si se lleva el 9 dentro de la raíz, debe entrar como 81, porque 9√7 = √(81 × 7) = √567. En cambio, √63 corresponde a √(9 × 7) = 3√7, que es menor que 9√7. Por eso, √63 no es equivalente.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>9</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>21</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La expresión original es 3√7 · 3 = 9√7. La opción 9√21 agrega un factor 3 dentro de la raíz, porque √21 = √(3 × 7), y eso cambia el valor. Al cuadrar ambas expresiones se obtiene 1701 para 9√21 y 567 para 9√7, así que no son equivalentes.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Escribir la expresión original</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión del enunciado es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:msqrt>
                    <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  </m:msqrt>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Reordenar los factores</strong></p>
            <p>Como se trata de una multiplicación, se pueden agrupar los números:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:msqrt>
                    <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  </m:msqrt>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:msqrt>
                    <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  </m:msqrt>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Multiplicar los factores numéricos</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>9</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:msqrt>
                    <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  </m:msqrt>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>9</m:mn>
                  <m:msqrt>
                    <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  </m:msqrt>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión obtenida es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>9</m:mn>
                  <m:msqrt>
                    <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                  </m:msqrt>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Esta coincide exactamente con la alternativa B.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión equivalente es <strong>la opción B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>